// README

** Check for the system Arch :
>> uname -a

** Get Hostname
>> hostname
>> hostnamectl hostname [name] 

// PASSWORD POLICY

** change pass : passwd
** man     : PAM_PWQUALITY
** Package : pam_cracklib
** config  : /etc/pam.d/common-password
** comand  : sudo chage --list

// PASSWORD EXPIRATION

** link    : https://www.redhat.com/sysadmin/password-expiration-date-linux
** config  : /etc/login.defs

// USER CRUD
useradd login
userdel login
list user : awk -F: '{ print $1}' /etc/passwd

// SUDO CONFIG
** man    : sudoers
